								<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Data continues to transcend industries as one of the most important skills a professional can have, in fact, the number of </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">data job openings</span><span style="font-weight: 400;"> is expected to reach 2,720,000 this year. </span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Getting a Data Certificate is a surefire way to elevate your technical skills to not only be more hireable but to use data to make better business decisions – and now you can do it from home!</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">We’ve rounded up five of the best data certificates worth your time.</span></p>
<div class="lead-grid-container">
<div class="lead__card">
<div class="lead__image"><img class="hide--mobile" src="https://d1jxdyr49kipv5.cloudfront.net/prod/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Data.jpg" alt="Icon"></div>
<div class="lead__content">
<p id="lead__heading" class="heading--4">Learn data skills to boost your career – from home!</p>
